;IF THE GEN ROUTINE NUMBER IS GIVEN AS A NEGATIVE NUMBER THEN VALUES WON'T BE NORMALIZED (RESCALED WITHIN THE RANGE -1 TO 1)

f 0 3600		;DUMMY SCORE EVENT - KEEPS REALTIME PERFORMANCE GOING FOR ONE HOUR
</CsScore>

